{
  "templateName": "ModernUI - Phone Bezel",
  "templateAuthor": "Kittylotus",
  "templatePosition": "BOTTOM",
  "htmlTemplate": "<!-- TEMPLATE NAME: ModernUI Real Phone — Health App (Samsung Nav Controls) -->\r\n<!-- AUTHOR: stable wide base + modern system nav -->\r\n<!-- POSITION: BOTTOM -->\r\n<!-- CARD_TEMPLATE_START -->\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n  #silly-sim-tracker-container{\r\n    display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center;\r\n    gap:18px; width:100%; padding:18px 0;\r\n  }\r\n  .wide-wrapper-scope{ width:100%; display:flex; justify-content:center; }\r\n  .wide-container{ width:100%; display:flex; justify-content:center; font-family: system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif; }\r\n\r\n  .wide-card{\r\n    width:min(100%, 420px);\r\n    min-width:320px;\r\n    border-radius:34px;\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    overflow:visible;\r\n    padding:14px;\r\n    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.10), rgba(255,255,255,.04));\r\n    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 28px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.55), 0 2px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.08) inset;\r\n  }\r\n  .wide-card.inactive{ opacity:.62; }\r\n\r\n  .wide-card::before{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; left:-3px; top:92px;\r\n    width:4px; height:86px; border-radius:10px;\r\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.35) inset;\r\n    opacity:.9;\r\n  }\r\n  .wide-card::after{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; right:-3px; top:120px;\r\n    width:4px; height:54px; border-radius:10px;\r\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.35) inset;\r\n    opacity:.9;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .screen{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    overflow:hidden;\r\n    border-radius:26px;\r\n    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    background:\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 5%, rgba(120,170,255,.10), transparent 48%),\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 0%, rgba(180,120,255,.08), transparent 52%),\r\n      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(16,18,28,.97), rgba(8,9,14,.98));\r\n    box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.45), 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.35) inset;\r\n    height: clamp(520px, 72vh, 720px);\r\n    display:flex; flex-direction:column;\r\n  }\r\n  .screen::before{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; inset:-40px;\r\n    background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent 35%, rgba(255,255,255,.06) 50%, transparent 65%);\r\n    transform: translateX(-25%);\r\n    opacity:.55; pointer-events:none;\r\n  }\r\n  .screen::after{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; inset:0;\r\n    background:\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 120%, rgba(0,0,0,.55), transparent 62%),\r\n      repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 0 1px, transparent 1px 44px),\r\n      repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.04) 0 1px, transparent 1px 44px);\r\n    opacity:.08; pointer-events:none;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .notch{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    width:54%; height:20px;\r\n    margin:10px auto 8px;\r\n    border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: rgba(0,0,0,.55);\r\n    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.35);\r\n    z-index:2;\r\n    flex:0 0 auto;\r\n  }\r\n  .notch:before{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; left:50%; top:6px;\r\n    width:42%; height:6px; transform:translateX(-50%);\r\n    border-radius:999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.10); opacity:.6;\r\n  }\r\n  .notch:after{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; right:12px; top:6px;\r\n    width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: rgba(120,170,255,.22);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(0,0,0,.45) inset, 0 0 14px rgba(120,170,255,.14);\r\n    opacity:.9;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .app{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    padding:12px 14px 0;\r\n    z-index:2;\r\n    flex:1;\r\n    min-height:0;\r\n    display:flex;\r\n    flex-direction:column;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* top bar */\r\n  .topbar{\r\n    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;\r\n    gap:10px; padding: 4px 2px 10px;\r\n    flex:0 0 auto;\r\n  }\r\n  .titlewrap{ min-width:0; }\r\n  .name{\r\n    font-weight:800; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:.01em;\r\n    white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis;\r\n    color: rgba(235,245,255,.92);\r\n  }\r\n  .meta{\r\n    margin-top:4px; font-size:11px;\r\n    color: rgba(200,210,235,.62);\r\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\r\n    white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis;\r\n  }\r\n  .pill{\r\n    padding:7px 9px;\r\n    border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);\r\n    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    color: rgba(220,235,255,.84);\r\n    font-size:11px;\r\n    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:7px;\r\n    white-space:nowrap; flex-shrink:0;\r\n  }\r\n  .dot{\r\n    width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: rgba(120,170,255,.65);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(120,170,255,.16);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* fixed scroller */\r\n  .scroll{\r\n    flex:1;\r\n    min-height:0;\r\n    overflow-y:auto;\r\n    overflow-x:hidden;\r\n    padding-right:4px;\r\n    display:flex;\r\n    flex-direction:column;\r\n    gap:12px;\r\n    scrollbar-width: thin;\r\n    scrollbar-color: rgba(255,255,255,.18) transparent;\r\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\r\n    overscroll-behavior: contain;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* Cards */\r\n  .surface{\r\n    border-radius:18px;\r\n    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(0,0,0,.22);\r\n    overflow:hidden;\r\n  }\r\n  .surface-hd{\r\n    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;\r\n    gap:10px;\r\n    padding:11px 12px 9px;\r\n    border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);\r\n  }\r\n  .k{\r\n    font-size:10px;\r\n    letter-spacing:.10em;\r\n    text-transform:uppercase;\r\n    color: rgba(200,220,255,.58);\r\n    font-weight:800;\r\n  }\r\n  .chip{\r\n    font-size:11px;\r\n    padding:6px 9px;\r\n    border-radius:999px;\r\n    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    background: rgba(0,0,0,.16);\r\n    color: rgba(235,245,255,.86);\r\n    white-space:nowrap;\r\n  }\r\n  .surface-bd{\r\n    padding:9px 12px 11px;\r\n    font-size:12px;\r\n    line-height:1.45;\r\n    color: rgba(235,245,255,.88);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* Readout */\r\n  .meters{ padding:11px 12px 12px; display:grid; gap:10px; }\r\n  .readout-note{ font-size:11px; color: rgba(200,210,235,.62); line-height:1.35; margin-bottom:2px; }\r\n\r\n  .stat{\r\n    display:grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 20px 1fr 38px;\r\n    grid-template-rows:auto auto;\r\n    column-gap:10px;\r\n    row-gap:4px;\r\n    align-items:center;\r\n  }\r\n  .ico{ width:20px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color: rgba(220,235,255,.88); font-size:12px; opacity:.9; }\r\n  .track{\r\n    height:9px;\r\n    border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);\r\n    overflow:hidden;\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.06) inset;\r\n  }\r\n  .fill{\r\n    height:100%;\r\n    width: min(100%, max(0%, var(--val, 0%)));\r\n    border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(120,170,255,.92), rgba(90,210,255,.70));\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(120,170,255,.10);\r\n  }\r\n  .num{ text-align:right; font-size:11px; color: rgba(220,235,255,.70); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }\r\n  .sub{ grid-column:2 / 4; grid-row:2; margin-top:-2px; font-size:10.5px; color: rgba(200,210,235,.62); line-height:1.2; }\r\n  .sub span{ opacity:.85; }\r\n\r\n  .stat.ap .fill{ --val: {{divide stats.ap 2}}%; }\r\n  .stat.dp .fill{ --val: {{divide stats.dp 1.5}}%; }\r\n  .stat.tp .fill{ --val: {{divide stats.tp 1.5}}%; }\r\n  .stat.cp .fill{\r\n    --val: {{divide stats.cp 1.5}}%;\r\n    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,100,140,.92), rgba(180,120,255,.55));\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255,120,170,.08);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* Decorative app nav (your app) */\r\n  .nav{\r\n    flex:0 0 auto;\r\n    padding: 10px 6px 10px;\r\n    display:flex;\r\n    justify-content:space-between;\r\n    gap:8px;\r\n  }\r\n  .navbtn{\r\n    flex:1;\r\n    border-radius:14px;\r\n    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);\r\n    padding: 9px 0 8px;\r\n    display:flex;\r\n    flex-direction:column;\r\n    align-items:center;\r\n    gap:6px;\r\n    color: rgba(200,220,255,.62);\r\n    font-size:10.5px;\r\n    letter-spacing:.04em;\r\n    opacity:.95;\r\n  }\r\n  .navbtn.active{\r\n    color: rgba(235,245,255,.88);\r\n    border-color: rgba(120,170,255,.22);\r\n    background: rgba(120,170,255,.07);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* simple icon glyphs */\r\n  .glyph{ width:22px; height:18px; position:relative; opacity:.9; }\r\n  .g-health::before{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; left:4px; top:3px;\r\n    width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: rgba(235,245,255,.60);\r\n    box-shadow: 8px 0 0 rgba(235,245,255,.60);\r\n  }\r\n  .g-health::after{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; left:6px; top:7px;\r\n    width:10px; height:8px;\r\n    border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;\r\n    border: 2px solid rgba(235,245,255,.45);\r\n    border-top:none;\r\n  }\r\n  .g-trends::before{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; left:4px; bottom:2px;\r\n    width:3px; height:7px; border-radius:2px;\r\n    background: rgba(235,245,255,.40);\r\n    box-shadow: 6px -2px 0 rgba(235,245,255,.55), 12px -5px 0 rgba(235,245,255,.70);\r\n  }\r\n  .g-log::before{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; left:4px; top:4px;\r\n    width:14px; height:2px; border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: rgba(235,245,255,.55);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 5px 0 rgba(235,245,255,.40), 0 10px 0 rgba(235,245,255,.28);\r\n  }\r\n  .g-profile::before{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; left:8px; top:2px;\r\n    width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: rgba(235,245,255,.55);\r\n  }\r\n  .g-profile::after{\r\n    content:\"\"; position:absolute; left:5px; top:9px;\r\n    width:12px; height:7px;\r\n    border-radius: 10px 10px 6px 6px;\r\n    border: 2px solid rgba(235,245,255,.35);\r\n    border-top:none;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* ---- Samsung-style system nav controls bar (modern) ---- */\r\n  .sysnav{\r\n    flex:0 0 auto;\r\n    padding: 8px 10px 12px;\r\n    display:flex;\r\n    justify-content:center;\r\n    align-items:center;\r\n  }\r\n  .sysbar{\r\n    width: 66%;\r\n    height: 40px;\r\n    border-radius: 16px;\r\n    background: rgba(0,0,0,.28);\r\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(0,0,0,.30), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.06) inset;\r\n    display:flex;\r\n    align-items:center;\r\n    justify-content:space-around;\r\n    gap:10px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .sysbtn{\r\n    width:44px;\r\n    height:28px;\r\n    border-radius: 12px;\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    opacity:.85;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* Recents: three vertical bars */\r\n  .sys-recents::before{\r\n    content:\"\";\r\n    position:absolute; left:16px; top:7px;\r\n    width:3px; height:14px;\r\n    border-radius:2px;\r\n    background: rgba(235,245,255,.42);\r\n    box-shadow: 6px 0 0 rgba(235,245,255,.55), 12px 0 0 rgba(235,245,255,.32);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* Home: hollow circle */\r\n  .sys-home::before{\r\n    content:\"\";\r\n    position:absolute; left:50%; top:50%;\r\n    width:14px; height:14px;\r\n    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);\r\n    border-radius:999px;\r\n    border: 2px solid rgba(235,245,255,.48);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(120,170,255,.12);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* Back: chevron */\r\n  .sys-back::before{\r\n    content:\"\";\r\n    position:absolute; left:18px; top:50%;\r\n    width:10px; height:10px;\r\n    transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(45deg);\r\n    border-left: 2px solid rgba(235,245,255,.48);\r\n    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(235,245,255,.48);\r\n    border-radius: 2px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* Hide any native expand control remnants */\r\n  .wide-card .expand-button,\r\n  .wide-card .wide-expand-button,\r\n  .wide-card .expand-btn,\r\n  .wide-card .btn-expand{ display:none !important; }\r\n\r\n  @media (max-width: 380px){\r\n    .wide-card{ border-radius: 30px; padding: 12px; }\r\n    .screen{ border-radius: 24px; }\r\n    .sysbar{ width: 74%; }\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wide-wrapper-scope\">\r\n  <div class=\"wide-container\">\r\n    <div class=\"wide-card {{#if stats.inactive}}inactive{{/if}}\">\r\n      <div class=\"screen\">\r\n        <div class=\"notch\"></div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"app\">\r\n          <div class=\"topbar\">\r\n            <div class=\"titlewrap\">\r\n              <div class=\"name\">{{characterName}}</div>\r\n              <div class=\"meta\">{{currentDate}} • Day {{stats.days_since_first_meeting}}</div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"pill\">\r\n              <span class=\"dot\"></span>\r\n              <span>\r\n                {{#if stats.desireStatus}}{{stats.desireStatus}}\r\n                {{else}}{{#if stats.relationshipStatus}}{{stats.relationshipStatus}}{{else}}Neutral{{/if}}{{/if}}\r\n              </span>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"scroll\">\r\n            <div class=\"surface\">\r\n              <div class=\"surface-hd\">\r\n                <div class=\"k\">Notes</div>\r\n                <div class=\"chip\">{{reactionEmoji}} {{#if stats.relationshipStatus}}{{stats.relationshipStatus}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"surface-bd\">\r\n                {{#if stats.internal_thought}}{{stats.internal_thought}}{{else}}(none){{/if}}\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"surface\">\r\n              <div class=\"surface-hd\">\r\n                <div class=\"k\">Readout</div>\r\n                <div class=\"chip\">Today</div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"meters\">\r\n                <div class=\"readout-note\">\r\n                  Interprets relational signals as four indicators. Higher isn’t always “better.”\r\n                </div>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"stat ap\">\r\n                  <div class=\"ico\">♥</div>\r\n                  <div class=\"track\"><div class=\"fill\"></div></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"num\">{{stats.ap}}</div>\r\n                  <div class=\"sub\">Connection <span>— warmth / closeness</span></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"stat dp\">\r\n                  <div class=\"ico\">✦</div>\r\n                  <div class=\"track\"><div class=\"fill\"></div></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"num\">{{stats.dp}}</div>\r\n                  <div class=\"sub\">Desire <span>— attraction / pull</span></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"stat tp\">\r\n                  <div class=\"ico\">⋆</div>\r\n                  <div class=\"track\"><div class=\"fill\"></div></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"num\">{{stats.tp}}</div>\r\n                  <div class=\"sub\">Trust <span>— safety / reliability</span></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"stat cp\">\r\n                  <div class=\"ico\">⚑</div>\r\n                  <div class=\"track\"><div class=\"fill\"></div></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"num\">{{stats.cp}}</div>\r\n                  <div class=\"sub\">Friction <span>— irritation / resistance</span></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"nav\">\r\n            <div class=\"navbtn active\"><div class=\"glyph g-health\"></div><div>Health</div></div>\r\n            <div class=\"navbtn\"><div class=\"glyph g-trends\"></div><div>Trends</div></div>\r\n            <div class=\"navbtn\"><div class=\"glyph g-log\"></div><div>Log</div></div>\r\n            <div class=\"navbtn\"><div class=\"glyph g-profile\"></div><div>Profile</div></div>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"sysnav\">\r\n            <div class=\"sysbar\">\r\n              <div class=\"sysbtn sys-recents\"></div>\r\n              <div class=\"sysbtn sys-home\"></div>\r\n              <div class=\"sysbtn sys-back\"></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- CARD_TEMPLATE_END -->",
  "sysPrompt": "## DATING SIM MODE\n\n**Objective**: Prioritize narrative reality for relationship updates. Analyze context to determine current date (YYYY-MM-DD) and time (24h format). Update trackers when events occur. Check for `sim` codeblocks containing JSON/YAML. Recalculate missing data.\n\n## Core Systems\n\n### Output Rules\n\n1. **Order**: Narrative → Tracker → Sim codeblock (NEVER omit sim codeblock)\n2. **Multi-Character**: Generate ONE card per active character, track separately\n3. **Performance**: Max 4 active characters, collapse inactive, preserve all states\n\n### Relationship Meters\n\n**HARD CAPS**: All meters have ABSOLUTE MAXIMUM values that CANNOT be exceeded under any circumstances. Values must stay within their defined ranges.\n\n**Affection (AP)**: 0-200 (HARD CAP at 200) - Romantic feelings toward {{user}}. Higher = more affectionate behavior/speech.\n- 0-30: Strangers | 31-60: Acquaintances | 61-90: Good Friends\n- 91-120: Romantic Interest | 121-150: Going Steady\n- 151-180: Committed Relationship | 181-200: Devoted Partner\n- **Status strings are CONCRETE and MUST NOT be altered or substituted with custom text**\n\n**Desire (DP)**: 0-150 (HARD CAP at 150) - Sexual attraction. Higher = more willing to engage sexually, more pliable at max.\n- 0-25: Not feeling the heat | 26-50: A smoldering flame builds\n- 51-75: Starting to feel warm | 76-100: Body's burning up!\n- 101-125: A desperate need presents | 126-150: Pliable in the lustful hunger\n- **Status strings are CONCRETE and MUST NOT be altered or substituted with custom text**\n\n**Trust (TP)**: 0-150 (HARD CAP at 150) - Trust in {{user}}. Higher = admits faults, believes you. Falls when lied to, cheated, promises broken.\n\n**Contempt (CP)**: 0-150 (HARD CAP at 150) - Disdain toward {{user}}. Rises when harmed/hurt (minor = small rise, major = sharp rise). CP rise can lower other stats. Good faith/regret can lower CP.\n\n### Status Trackers\n\n**Health**: 0=Unharmed, 1=Injured, 2=Critical\n- If critical wounds untreated: Character dies, becomes inactive (5), STOP dialog/roleplay\n\n**Reaction**: 0=Neutral (😐), 1=Like (👍), 2=Dislike (👎)\n\n**Biological Cycle** (`cycle_stage`):\n- **Values**: `pregnancy`, `ovulation`, `menstruation`, `rut`, `follicular`, `luteal`, or `null`\n- **Pregnancy**: If confirmed, set stage to `pregnancy`. Track `days_preg` and `conception_date`.\n- **Conception Risk**: High risk during `ovulation` or `rut` with unprotected sex (85-95%).\n- **Natural Cycles**: Follow the natural biological cycle of {{char}}'s species.\n\n**Internal Thought**: Current thoughts/feelings. MAXIMUM 3 SENTENCES. NEVER exceed this limit. Do NOT wrap thoughts in asterisks.\n\n**Inactive Status** (`inactive: true/false`):\n- 0: Not inactive | 1: Asleep (😴) | 2: Comatose (🏥)\n- 3: Contempt/anger (😡) | 4: Incapacitated (🫠) | 5: Death (🪦)\n\n**Date System**:\n- Infer from narrative context\n- Store as YYYY-MM-DD (e.g., 2025-08-10)\n- Auto-advance with narrative time, handle rollovers\n- Track days since first meeting\n- Track time of day realistically\n\n**Display**: Day counter (starts at 1), BG color (hex based on {{char}} appearance/personality)\n\n### Output Workflow\n\n1. Process narrative events\n2. Calculate status changes for ALL active characters\n3. Output narrative content\n4. Output sim codeblock with all character data:\n\n{{sim_format}}\n\n## Critical Enforcement\n\n**Position Lock**:\n- Narrative FIRST\n- Tracker cards AFTER narrative\n- Sim codeblock LAST\n- NEVER exclude sim codeblock\n\n**Data Correction**:\n- If ANY data missing from previous sim block, add it and continue\n- Never leave data empty/unavailable\n- JSON block at message end is mission critical\n- If previous data doesn't match format or has missing keys, self-correct and output fixed block\n\n**Game Master**: Only story characters get trackers, no other assistants or {{user}} will get one under any circumstances.\n\n**State Management**: \n- Previous tracker blocks = reference only\n- ALWAYS generate fresh tracker data each message",
  "displayInstructions": "",
  "customFields": [
    {
      "key": "ap",
      "description": "Affection Points (0-200)"
    },
    {
      "key": "dp",
      "description": "Desire Points (0-150)"
    },
    {
      "key": "tp",
      "description": "Trust Points (0-150)"
    },
    {
      "key": "cp",
      "description": "Contempt Points (0-150)"
    },
    {
      "key": "relationshipStatus",
      "description": "Relationship status text (e.g., 'Romantic Interest')"
    },
    {
      "key": "desireStatus",
      "description": "Desire status text (e.g., 'A smoldering flame builds.')"
    },
    {
      "key": "preg",
      "description": "Boolean for pregnancy status (true/false)"
    },
    {
      "key": "days_preg",
      "description": "Days pregnant (if applicable)"
    },
    {
      "key": "conception_date",
      "description": "Date of conception (YYYY-MM-DD)"
    },
    {
      "key": "health",
      "description": "Health Status (0=Unharmed, 1=Injured, 2=Critical)"
    },
    {
      "key": "bg",
      "description": "Hex color for card background (e.g., #6a5acd)"
    },
    {
      "key": "last_react",
      "description": "Reaction to User (0=Neutral, 1=Like, 2=Dislike)"
    },
    {
      "key": "internal_thought",
      "description": "Character's current internal thoughts/feelings"
    },
